<plot>When Helping Hurts tells the harrowing stories of trauma workers from around the world and how Secondary Traumatization and Compassion Fatigue invaded their lives. This film sensitively presents insight on preventing or reducing these effects and presents a light at the end of the recovery tunnel.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?652844</url></doc>
